# Margot autonomous evidence logs are append-only and are written from many
# parallel branches/worktrees. Mark them merge=union so Git auto-resolves
# overlapping appends by keeping BOTH sides instead of producing conflict
# markers. This prevents the recurring morning-report.md / overnight-progress-log.md
# merge conflicts (and the markers that previously got committed into them).
**/margot/morning-report.md merge=union
**/margot/overnight-progress-log.md merge=union
